{"tid":468463,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［2018DSE] 英文科討論區","createTime":"2017-11-14T11:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T02:50:11.000Z","uid":11058,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8926c505b9404899a8ef5cdf7cad68cb2de15c6b","tid":468463,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:42:47.000Z","msg":"上年考英文科之前<br />\n試過想每日share有關英文既野<br />\n點知太忙<del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">同埋太懶</span></del>放棄左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是今年一於重新黎過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">盡量</span></del>唔爛尾<br />\n陪大家一齊考DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每日我都會分享關於英文同埋英文科既知識<br />\n英文既subject knowlegde會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n考英文科既skill又會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而保障我自己學生既利益<br />\n我會先係自己<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">instagram: awenglishls</span>分享<br />\n然後三日後再share上黎連登<br />\n換言之連登會有三日delay<br />\n但係係依個post<br />\n保證唔會有商業成份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有需要既同學可以follow IG <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連登巴打絲打仲可以send作文去email: awtutorial @hotmail.com <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只改電子版及掃描版（用電話影相唔計架吓）<br />\n記住email入面寫番個連登名<br />\n同埋幫我推一推post呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事不宜遲 馬上開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720aaeaeb8a3f60b2e737464361b7f690a57c972","tid":468463,"uid":11058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/194449_038578e59eaf8922298d5e5cc43cc47f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F194449_038578e59eaf8922298d5e5cc43cc47f.jpg&h=a62c8b57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《Intolerable Mistakes 1️⃣》<br />\n👉🏻Seek v.s. Search for👈🏻<br />\n<br />\n早幾日，喺Facebook見到有個大型補習社拎住幾個學位既English Tutor，佢share左一個佢寫既 column（欄目）<br />\n<br />\n一睇就嚇死我<br />\n<br />\nSeek 係 transitive verb（及物動詞）<br />\n即係話後面直接就跟noun（名詞）<br />\n而Seek後面永遠都唔會跟for！<br />\n<br />\nSeek有1️⃣尋找/尋覓2️⃣征求既意思<br />\n除左Search for係都有尋找既意思<br />\n類似既字仲有look for / hunt for<br />\n<br />\n又或者代表征求既時候<br />\nSynonyms有ask for / solicit<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為多幾個學位<br />\n英文水平一定好喇"},{"pid":"0f8e1b83be7e130c352745baa2a3a11e43ee2eb3","tid":468463,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:47:15.000Z","msg":"lm學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8058454983ab94f3057b899cf33538b7721923b","tid":468463,"uid":152244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:48:31.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"1bab26f2d9895542723f57ebf74843a482876e3d","tid":468463,"uid":33390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:07:31.000Z","msg":"Dse雞留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ad05a303fc987ff30dbfd4279f0a389f71de85","tid":468463,"uid":60115,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:09:26.000Z","msg":"點解要咁傻仔去認真考dse英文<br />\n讀asso輕鬆走後門入3大好過啦"},{"pid":"6f3cbcaa4d7a6459f5808b82f6be14eb90b103a2","tid":468463,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:12:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要咁傻仔去認真考dse英文<br />\n讀asso輕鬆走後門入3大好過啦</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dfd1b716175e7cf2f29be8eca669f0de31ed2e8","tid":468463,"uid":8487,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:25:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"h